    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Buildings or parts of buildings housing facilities for use by the employees for activities not strictly required for the job, such as a break room, meeting rooms, lockers, human resources offices, etc.</Note_Text>
